{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2013}} {{BLP sources|date=April 2010}} {{Infobox musical artist | name = Andrea Brown | image = | alt = | caption = | image_size = | background = solo_singer | birth_name = | alias = | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|1974|2|17}} | birth_place = [[Boston, Massachusetts]] | instrument = [[Vocals]] | occupation = [[Singing|Singer]] | years_active = 2002 | label = [[AM PM Records|AM:PM]], Groovilicious, Popular }} '''Andrea Brown''' (born 17 February 1974) is an [[African American]] female singer from [[Boston, Massachusetts]]. She is also the cousin of singer [[Bobby Brown]].
